  m_text: "Jump on rocks to radiocarbon sample them.\n\nYou only want to sample the
    right rocks. Look for tufa, not soil carbonate. Make sure you don't walk too
    far up or down from this shoreline. \n\nWatch out for rattlesnakes and tumbleweeds,
    they will slow you down!"
